# CLIP ChangeLog for <sys-libs/pam>

*pam-1.1.8-r4 (25 Feb 2016)

  25 Feb 2016; Timothée Ravier <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +pam-1.1.8-r4.ebuild, -pam-1.1.8-r3.ebuild:
  RBump to force update after pambase update effectively fixing the
  /etc/pam.d/login conflict.

*pam-1.1.8-r3 (25 Feb 2016)

  25 Feb 2016; Timothée Ravier <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +pam-1.1.8-r3.ebuild, -pam-1.1.8-r2.ebuild:
  RBump to force updating after shadow-4.1.5.1-r4, which fixes the conflict
  with pambase (/etc/pam.d/login) in SDKs.

  19 Feb 2016; ANSSI <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  pam-1.1.8-r2.ebuild, files/access.conf.clip:
  Migrate from clip-tiny to clip-bare.

